+	/* ACPM/cal-if DVFS clocks for the GPU (G3D shader + G3DL2), exposed to
+	 * the common clk framework so the open Panthor driver can bind them via
+	 * clocks = <&gpu_clk 0>, <&gpu_clk 1>. Driver: clk-acpm-gpu.c. Kbase
